  "difficulty": 1.5,
  "summary": "发现函数的本质是 $(x | y) - y = (x \\& \\sim y)$，然后就秒杀这题了。",
  "link": "https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/CF1299A",
  "link_text": "CF1299A Anu Has a Function - 洛谷",
  "source": "",
  "aliases": [],
  "parent": null,
  "format": "logseq",
  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "题目描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "Anu 创建了她自己的函数 $f$：$f(x, y) = (x | y) - y$，其中 $|$ 表示<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bitwise_operation#OR\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"md-link\">按位或运算</a>。例如，$f(11, 6) = (11|6) - 6 = 15 - 6 = 9$。可以证明，对于任意非负整数 $x$ 和 $y$，$f(x, y)$ 的值也是非负的。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "她想进一步研究这个函数，并为自己设计了多个问题。但她无法解决所有问题，需要你的帮助。以下是其中一个问题。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "一个数组 $[a_1, a_2, \\dots, a_n]$ 的“值”被定义为 $f(f(\\dots f(f(a_1, a_2), a_3), \\dots, a_{n-1}), a_n)$（见下方注释）。给定一个不一定互不相同的数组，你可以重新排列其元素。请问应如何重新排列数组，使其“值”最大？",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "输入描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "第一行包含一个整数 $n$（$1 \\le n \\le 10^5$）。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "第二行包含 $n$ 个整数 $a_1, a_2, \\ldots, a_n$（$0 \\le a_i \\le 10^9$）。数组中的元素不保证互不相同。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "输出描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "输出 $n$ 个整数，为使数组“值”最大的重新排列结果。如果有多种答案，输出任意一种均可。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "样例",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "输入 1",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "code",
              "lang": "",
              "code": "4\n4 0 11 6",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "输出 1",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "code",
              "lang": "",
              "code": "11 6 4 0",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "输入 2",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "code",
              "lang": "",
              "code": "1\n13",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "输出 2",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "code",
              "lang": "",
              "code": "13",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "样例说明",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "在第一个测试样例中，数组 $[11, 6, 4, 0]$ 的值为 $f(f(f(11, 6), 4), 0) = f(f(9, 4), 0) = f(9, 0) = 9$。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$[11, 4, 0, 6]$ 也是一个合法答案。",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "void solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tint n; cin >> n;\n\tvar a = vector<int>(n + 1);\n\tvar cnt = vector<int>(31);\n\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tcin >> a[i];\n\t\tfa(j, 0, 30)if (!(a[i] & (1 << j)))cnt[j]++;\n\t}\n\tint ans = 0, mx = -1;\n\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tint mask = 0;\n\t\tfa(j, 0, 30) {\n\t\t\tif (a[i] & (1 << j)) {\n\t\t\t\tif (cnt[j] == n - 1)\n\t\t\t\t\tmask |= (1 << j);\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\telse {\n\t\t\t\tif (cnt[j] - 1 == n - 1)\n\t\t\t\t\tmask |= (1 << j);\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\t\tint now = (a[i] & mask);\n\t\tif (mx < now) {\n\t\t\tmx = now;\n\t\t\tans = i;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tcout << a[ans] << ' ';\n\tfa(i, 1, n)if (i != ans)cout << a[i] << ' ';\n\tcout << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
